Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.86,0:23:34.63,ed_BD_11,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm following you everywhere you go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:39.14,ed_BD_11,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Still…
