Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:58.25,ed_BD_11,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm soaked in tears everywhere I go
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.02,0:24:04.70,ed_BD_11,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Caught up in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:10.28,ed_BD_11,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Like in a daydream
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.51,0:24:14.39,ed_BD_11,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I feel you smile
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:20.66,ed_BD_11,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}But I wake up to a lonely dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.66,0:24:25.17,ed_BD_11,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}To know you're gone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.95,0:24:32.03,ed_BD_11,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My endless love…
